commands.name: az providerhub resource-type-registration delete
commands.syntax:
az providerhub resource-type-registration delete [--ids]
                                                 [--name]
                                                 [--no-wait {0, 1, f, false, n, no, t, true, y, yes}]
                                                 [--provider-namespace]
                                                 [--subscription]
                                                 [--yes]
